ami]]| accessdate = 2007-09-06}}</ref>\n* First Castlevania game with online cooperative multiplayer.\n* Popular game outlets included a 20th Anniversary Pre-Order Bundle with the game.<ref>{{cite web| author = Brendan Sinclair| date = 2006-10-23| work = [[GameSpot]]| url = http://www.gamespot.com/ds/action/castlevaniaportraitofruin/news.html?sid=6160362| title = Konami boxes DS Castlevania| accessdate = 2007-05-03}}</ref>\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article= Castlevania: Order of Shadows\n|title= Castlevania: Order of Shadows\n|date= {{Video game release|NA|September 18, 2007}}\n|refs= <ref name=\"IGNOoS\">{{cite web| url = http://wireless.ign.com/objects/958/958506.html| title = Castlevania: Order of Shadows| work = IGN| accessdate = 2007-10-02| url-status = dead| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071003192653/http://wireless.ign.com/objects/958/958506.html| archivedate = 2007-10-03}}</ref>\n|release= 2007 \u2013 Mobile phone\n|notes= * Developed and published by Konami Mobile.<ref name=\"IGNOoS\"/>\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article= Castlevania: Order of Ecclesia\n|title= Castlevania: Order of Ecclesia\n|date= {{Video game release|NA|October 21, 2008|JP|October 23, 2008|EU|February 6, 2009}}\n|refs= <ref name=\"ooe_release-date_na\">{{cite web|date = 2008-07-31|url=http://www.gamespot.com/ds/action/castlevaniaorderofecclesia/index.html|title=GameSpot: Castlevania: Order of Ecclesia|work=[[GameSpot]]|accessdate=2008-07-31}}</ref><ref name=\"ooe_release-date_jp\">{{cite web|date = 2008-07-25|url=http://www.konami.jp/gs/game/dracula_ds3|title=The second Promotional Video reveals japanese release date and the names of characters|publisher=[[Konami|Konami Digital Entertainment Co., Ltd.]]|accessdate=2008-07-26}}</ref>\n|release= 2008 \u2013 Nintendo DS\n|notes= * Known in Japan as {{nihongo|''Akumaj\u014d Dracula Ubawareta Kokuin''|\u60aa\u9b54\u57ce\u30c9\u30e9\u30ad\u30e5\u30e9 \u596a\u308f\u308c\u305f\u523b\u5370|Akumaj\u014d Dorakyura Ubawareta 