i Announces Castlevania: Lords of Shadow |url=http://www.konami.com/news/article52.php |publisher=[[Konami]] |accessdate=2009-05-14 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607100904/http://www.konami.com/news/article52.php |archivedate=2009-06-07 }}</ref>\n* Developed by [[MercurySteam]] and [[Kojima Productions]] instead of [[Koji Igarashi]].<ref name=\"LordsOfShadow\"/>\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article=\n|title= Pachislot Akumaj\u014d Dracula III\n|date= {{Video game release|JP|February 6, 2012}}\n|refs=<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kpenet.jp/kpe_ad/dracula_Blog.html#blog120206|title=KPE blog|language=Japanese|publisher=Kpenet.jp|accessdate=2013-06-13|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326180747/http://www.kpenet.jp/kpe_ad/dracula_Blog.html#blog120206|archivedate=2012-03-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kpenet.jp/ps_2012.html|title=KPE 2012 games|language=Japanese|publisher=Kpenet.jp|accessdate=2013-06-13|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515004627/http://www.kpenet.jp/ps_2012.html|archivedate=2013-05-15}}</ref>\n|release= 2012 \u2013.[[Slot machine]]\n|notes= * A prequel to ''Pachislot Akumaj\u014d Dracula''.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kpenet.jp/contents/dracula3.html |title=KPE \u30d1\u30c1\u30b9\u30ed\u300e\u60aa\u9b54\u57ce\u30c9\u30e9\u30ad\u30e5\u30e9\u2162\u300fOFFICIAL SITE |work=Kpenet.jp |accessdate=2012-08-14 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120616140301/http://www.kpenet.jp/contents/dracula3.html |archivedate=2012-06-16 }}</ref>\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article=Castlevania: Lords of Shadow \u2013 Mirror of Fate\n|title= Castlevania: Lords of Shadow \u2013 Mirror of Fate\n|date= {{Video game release|NA|March 5, 2013|EU|March 8, 2013|JP|March 20, 2013}}\n|refs=\n|release= 2013 \u2013 [[Nintendo 3DS]], [[Xbox 360]], [[PlayStation 3]]<br>2014 \u2013 [[Microsoft Windows]]\n|notes= * Sequel to [[Castlevania: Lords of Shadow|Lords of S