aniasymphonyoftn/index.html?tag=result;title;1| title=Castlevania: Symphony of the Night for PS|work=[[GameSpot]]|accessdate=2007-10-12}}</ref><ref name=\"C-SotN\">{{cite web| url = http://au.gamespot.com/ps/adventure/castlevaniasymphonyoftn/similar.html?mode=versions| title = Castlevania: Symphony of the Night&nbsp;\u2013 Release Summary| work = [[GameSpot]]| accessdate = 2007-09-11| url-status = dead| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110721045955/http://au.gamespot.com/ps/adventure/castlevaniasymphonyoftn/similar.html?mode=versions| archivedate = 2011-07-21}}</ref>\n|release= 1997 \u2013 PlayStation<ref name=\"C-SotN\"/><br>1998 \u2013 [[Sega Saturn]]<ref>{{cite web| url = http://cheats.gamespy.com/saturn/castlevania-x/| title = Castlevania: Symphony of the Night (Saturn)| work = [[GameSpy]]| accessdate = 2007-09-11| url-status = dead| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071017074652/http://cheats.gamespy.com/saturn/castlevania-x/| archivedate = 2007-10-17}}</ref><br>2007 \u2013 [[Xbox Live Arcade]], PlayStation Network, PlayStation Portable (''Castlevania: The Dracula X Chronicles'')<ref>{{cite web| title = Sony reprises Symphony of the Night| url = http://au.gamespot.com/xbox360/adventure/castlevaniasotn/news.html?sid=6175445| author = Brendan Sinclair| work = [[GameSpot]]| date = 2007-07-20| accessdate = 2007-09-11| url-status = dead| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110721050021/http://au.gamespot.com/xbox360/adventure/castlevaniasotn/news.html?sid=6175445| archivedate = 2011-07-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/previewPage?cId=3156904|title=Castlevania: The Dracula X Chronicles (PSP)|first=Jeremy|last=Parish|date=2007-02-01|work=[[1UP.com]]|accessdate=2007-09-04|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927213601/http://www.1up.com/do/previewPage?cId=3156904|archivedate=2007-09-27}}</ref><br>2020 - [[Android (operating system)|Android]], [[iOS]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gematsu.com/2020/03/