\u30ad\u30e5\u30e9|publisher=Pachiseven|language=Japanese|accessdate=2016-06-08}}</ref>\n|release= 2015 \u2013 Slot machine\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article=\n|title=Pachislot Akumaj\u014d Dracula: Lords of Shadow\n|date={{Video game release|JP|April 6, 2017}}\n|refs=\n|release= 2017 \u2013 Slot machine\n}}\n}}\n}}\n\n===Compilations and collections===\n{{Video game titles|\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article=\n|title= Konami Collector's Series: Castlevania & Contra\n|date= {{Video game release|NA|November 16, 2002}}\n|refs= <ref name=\"CastlevaniaAndContra\"/>\n|release= 2002 \u2013 Microsoft Windows\n|notes= * The compilation includes the NES versions of ''[[Castlevania (1986 video game)|Castlevania]]'', ''[[Castlevania II: Simon's Quest]]'', and ''[[Castlevania III: Dracula's Curse]]'' along with ''[[Contra (video game)|Contra]]'' and ''[[Super Contra|Super C]]''.\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article=\n|title= Castlevania: Double Pack\n|date= {{Video game release|NA|January 11, 2006|EU|February 17, 2006}}\n|refs= <ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.gamespot.com/gba/action/castlevaniadoublepack/similar.html?mode=versions| title = Castlevania Double Pack| work = [[GameSpot]]| accessdate = 2007-10-25}}</ref>\n|release= 2006 \u2013 Game Boy Advance\n|notes= * A single Game Boy Advance cartridge that includes ''[[Castlevania: Harmony of Dissonance]]'' and ''[[Castlevania: Aria of Sorrow]]''.<ref name=\"DoublePack\"/>\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|article= Castlevania: Rondo of Blood#Castlevania: The Dracula X Chronicles|Castlevania: The Dracula X Chronicles\n|title= Castlevania: The Dracula X Chronicles\n|date= {{Video game release|JP|November 8, 2007|NA|October 23, 2007|[[EUR]]|February 15, 2008}}\n|refs= <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/psp/action/castlevaniathedraculaxchronicles/similar.html?mode=versions |title=Castlevania: The Dracula X Chronicles&nbsp;\u2013 Release Summary |work=[[GameSpot]] |accessdate=2007-10-25 |url-status=dead |archiveu