}}\n| [[Konami]]\n|<ref name=\"CTV2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.squareenixmusic.com/albums/d/draculatribute2.shtml |title=Akumajo Dracula Tribute Vol. 2 |work=Square Enix Music Online|accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref>\n|- style=\"text-align: center;\"\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''Castlevania: Harmony of Despair OST''\n| {{dts|January 13, 2011}}\n| {{sort|11656|1:16:56}}\n| [[Konami]]\n|<ref name=\"CHODOST\">{{cite web|url=http://www.squareenixmusic.com/albums/d/draculaharmonydespair.shtml |title=Akumajo Dracula Harmony of Despair Original Soundtrack |work=Square Enix Music Online|accessdate=2013-02-05}}</ref>\n|- style=\"text-align: center;\"\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''Pachislot Akumajo Dracula III OST''\t\n| February 22, 2012\t\n| 1:13:44\n| [[Konami]]\t\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.konamistyle.jp/item/71660 |title=\u30b3\u30ca\u30df\u30b9\u30bf\u30a4\u30eb \uff1a \u30d1\u30c1\u30b9\u30ed\u60aa\u9b54\u57ce\u30c9\u30e9\u30ad\u30e5\u30e9III ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACK\uff08CD\uff09 &#124; KONAMI STYLE |publisher=Konamistyle.jp |date= |accessdate=2015-12-24}}</ref>\n|- style=\"text-align: center;\"\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''Castlevania: Lords of Shadow \u2013 Ultimate Edition Soundtrack''\t\n| February 22, 2012\t\n| 1:10:21<br>1:43:27{{efn|Some songs of the soundtrack are exclusively available through the official website of [[Sumthing Distribution]].}}\n| [[Konami]]\t\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sumthing.com/p/castlevania-lords-of-shadow/ |title=Castlevania: Lords of Shadow &#124; Game Soundtracks, Latest Releases, Hot Items, Award Winning, Horror, ROCKtober |publisher=Sumthing |date=2013-10-29 |accessdate=2015-12-24 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224053253/http://www.sumthing.com/p/castlevania-lords-of-shadow/ |archivedate=2015-12-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Castlevania-Shadow-Ultimate-Edition-Soundtrack/dp/B00G4ABM9S/ref=tmm_other_meta_binding_tit