son \u2013 mixing assistant\n* [[John Fort\u00e9]] \u2013 performer\n* Jay Nicholas \u2013 mixing assistant\n* [[Pras]] \u2013 performer, executive producer\n* [[Melky Sedeck]] \u2013 performer\n* [[New York Philharmonic Orchestra]] \u2013 performer\n* Tomas Muscionico \u2013 photography\n* [[Mike Roach]] \u2013 mixing assistant\n* Storm Jefferson \u2013 mixing assistant\n* Paul Epworth \u2013 assistant engineer\n* Brian Dozoretz \u2013 engineer, mixing assistant\n* [[Jocelyne B\u00e9roard]] \u2013 performer\n* [[Sweet Micky]] \u2013 performer\n* [[The Neville Brothers]] \u2013 performer\n* [[Celia Cruz]] \u2013 performer\n\n==Charts==\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Chart (1997-1998)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n|[[Canadian Albums Chart|Canadian RPM Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bac-lac.gc.ca/eng/discover/films-videos-sound-recordings/rpm/Pages/item.aspx?IdNumber=2171&|publisher=[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]] |title=Top Albums/CDs - Volume 66, No. 26 |date=March 23, 1998|accessdate=June 2, 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|42\n|-\n|[[MegaCharts|Dutch Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dutchcharts.nl/weekchart.asp?year=1998&date=19980411&cat=a|title=Dutch Album Top 100|date=April 11, 1998|accessdate=June 2, 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|48\n|-\n|[[Media Control Charts|German Albums Chart]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|81\n|-\n|[[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand|New Zealand Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://charts.nz/weekchart.asp?year=1998&date=19980531&cat=a|title=New Zealand Album Top 40 |date=May 31, 1998|accessdate=June 2, 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|31\n|-\n|[[VG-lista|Norwegian Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://norwegiancharts.com/weekchart.asp?year=1997&date=199728&cat=a|title=VG Lista - Album Top 40|accessdate=June 2, 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|24\n|-\n|[[Sverigetopplistan|Swedish Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://